      "content": "but that's the thing... being myself doesn't change the fact that people don't get it. it's not just about \"pressure,\" it's like there's a fundamental gap between me and the rest of the world. it's like i'm constantly running on a battery that won't charge. what's even the point of trying to find peace if the world itself is just this loud, exhausting place that's never gonna make sense to me?",
